en.description:
Exciting Short Dramas at Your Fingertips! Hope these works bring you different experiences~

#AncestorDescending #PopularShortDramas #ShortDramaRecommendations #NewDramaArrival #Revenge #FeelGoodNovel #Urban #Fantasy #Cultivation #WealthyFamily #UrbanRomance #UrbanCultivation #GlobalPremiere #ExclusiveShortDrama #OfficialAuthorization #MasterDescending #UrbanDailyLife #LatestShortDrama #Historical #AncientCostume #SecretIdentity #Wealthy #FaceSlapping #PlotTwist #StrongReturn #Invincible #Drama #ChineseDrama

Drama Name: "The Ancestor Descends the Mountain"
Plot:
The 800-year-old ancestor, Ye Wuqie, descends the mountain to marry when a love tribulation approaches. He is mistaken for a scammer by the Ye family descendants. At the engagement banquet, his true identity is finally revealed, stunning everyone!

Ye Wuqie, the patriarch of the Ye family, has lived from the Zhu Yuanzhang period to the present, already 800 years old. He has been living on the mountain with his elderly descendants. Due to the impending love tribulation, Ye Wuqie is forced to descend and marry the world's most beautiful woman, Su Qingmei.
The Ye family descendants have never seen Ye Wuqie before, and when they greet him, they mistake him for a conman, Sun Zhong. Su Qingmei also mistakes Sun Zhong for her fiancÃ©.
Su Qingmei, who is frail and sickly, accidentally faints and runs into Ye Wuqie, who heals her.
Su Qingmei secretly develops feelings for him, but because of the power of the Ye family, she is still expected to marry into the Ye family.
At the engagement banquet, a mix-up occurs where no one believes Ye Wuqieâ€™s identity. Finally, the financial magnate Ye Haicheng proves that Ye Wuqie is indeed the real Ye family patriarch, and the Ye family descendants realize the huge mistake they made.
The Du family has always coveted the Ye familyâ€™s position, and they cause trouble during the engagement banquet. The Du family dares to act because they also have an ancestor, from whom they obtained divine skills and poison.
However, Du Lei does not know that Ye Wuqie is actually the Du family's ancestor. Ye Wuqie makes Du Lei face the consequences of his actions, and Du Lei is imprisoned in a death cell.
After overcoming many hardships, Ye Wuqie and Su Qingmei finally come together.

snippet.title: Who's gonna pop the balloon first?
snippet.description:
SUBSCRIBE & ADOPT A KATANA WITH THE LINK IN BIO!! 

If you love katana unboxing, then you'll love this. See the Katanas slice in action as satisfying as ASMR! These aren't rusted katanas! Sword-making, blacksmithing, knife making, and katana making are Mini Katana's passions! If you love anime like One Piece, Naruto, Demon Slayer, Attack on Titan, Miira No Kaikata, Mugen Train, Jujutsu Kaisen, sword art online abridged, slice of life anime, chainsaw man vs katana, afro samurai and are excited about the Swordsmith arc, you're gonna love our ninja weapons! Mini Katana is the founding titan of katana making, knife making, and the mini katana keychain. Learn how to draw a katana and how to make kunai like Naruto. We are the last samurai. We love Japanese anime, Japanese history, Japanese lofi, Japanese movies, and Japanese songs. Subscribe to watch mini katana unboxing, how to make a katana with cardboard and with paper, and more!  The Mini Katana Store is committed to high quality carbon steel blades and giving you slice of life looks as we try not to laugh challenge. Trust, Mini Katana knows how to make kunai and how to make a sword!

en.description:
THE FIRST TAKE is a YouTube Channel dedicated to filming musicians and singers performing in a single take.

Episode 521 marks the first appearance of CRYCHIC from BanG Dream!, a mix media project spanning TV anime, games, comics, and live performances showcasing voice actors on stage. The 5-piece band who reunited in the latest episode of the anime series will perform â€œHaruhikage,â€ a track featured in the 2023 TV anime BanG Dream! Itâ€™s MyGO!!!!!, that played a pivotal role in its storyline.
Enjoy the one-shot performance of this track featuring heartfelt lyrics that portray a withdrawn heart blossoming under the warmth of spring sunshine called friendship, merging with a refreshing and vibrant band sound, exclusively on THE FIRST TAKE.
